name: Ghibli - Nausicaa (Nausicaä of the Valley of the Wind (film))
description:
f you happen to be fond of the LoRa, I cordially invite you to share your wonderfully crafted images in this space, while also considering leaving behind a heartfelt review (or even just a rating) to bolster motivation and whatnot

This film evokes a flood of cherished memories... It holds a special place in my heart as the very first anime movie I experienced on the big screen.
"Nausicaä of the Valley of the Wind" is a captivating journey. As I immersed myself in collecting training data, I couldn't help but notice fascinating details that enriched the viewing experience.



You can join this discord to share your creations and your lora or see those of others : https://discord.gg/FZqYYGk82W
